{"tid":1530648,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳帆：警隊以專業態度維持法治 出現在港鐵站正常不過","createTime":"2019-09-02T04:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T06:12:38.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fe9119350282b388f976e41899612fc77c3752","tid":1530648,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:18:42.000Z","msg":"政府召開跨部門記者會，運輸及房屋局局長陳帆被問到，今早有網民發起在港鐵站「不合作運動」，多個港鐵站都有警員預先到場，是否是港鐵要求，陳帆回應指，警隊是維持法治的團隊，以專業態度處理事情，警方有鐵路警察，警員出現在港鐵站是正常不過的事。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，港鐵職員都是文職，遇到暴力情況要有警員到場，大家不應該將警察放在對立面，因為警察是本港法治守護者，如果大家對警隊執法有不理想和不同意的問題，是有機制處理，包括監警會及投訴警察課，都會公正處理。<br />\n<br />\n保安局局長李家超補充稱，警員到港鐵站是做預防性工作，收到情報警方會按需要部署，亦是按照警隊條例去做。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2237861/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2237861%2F&d=nh4ioWg9Uual2b2uu0vi%2FYjkqoP0ISDA%2F8fQ3RVu%2FF4%3D&h=d447161c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2237861/</a>"},{"pid":"45c6b0f40075c92e182514783708891a25500761","tid":1530648,"uid":55130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"721?"},{"pid":"3029e44df138a166bb7f80482afe5cf7009fb998","tid":1530648,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T04:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/01/223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2F223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif&h=16fdca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民學唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>&quot;The Star-Spangled Banner&quot;</em><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a